sql:
SELECT g.gene_id, g.locus_tag, g.description 
FROM genes g 
WHERE g.gene_id NOT IN (SELECT gene_id FROM gene_expression_values);

SELECT AVG(expression_value) AS average_expression_value
FROM gene_expression_values
WHERE gene_id = (SELECT gene_id FROM genes WHERE locus_tag = 'gene_001');

SELECT DISTINCT description
FROM genes
WHERE gene_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- The term 'overall average expression value for all genes' refers to the average expression value of all genes across all growth conditions; 
- 'identifiers' includes gene_id, locus_tag, and cluster_id; 
- 'other information' includes the average expression value for the gene and the description of the gene.
